  "title": "Waiter/Waitress",
  "description": "<p><strong>Application Mode</strong></p><ul><li>Apply by Whatsapp <strong>+65 85229666</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Meet, greet and lead customers to their seats</li><li>Accountable for the smooth running of designated area</li><li>Replenish cutleries as and when necessary</li><li>Ensure that tables under have the correct cutleries and table settings</li><li>Serve food and beverage orders</li><li>Reset tables after use (i.e. clear and remove soiled dishes)</li><li>Adhere to the standards operations procedures and suggest improvements to the superiors</li><li>Maintain consistent best-in-class service and good hygiene standards</li><li>Maintain good work performance and professional grooming standards</li><li>Monitor quality of all food and beverage items served</li><li>Attend all pre-service meetings/roll-call</li><li>Provide a courteous and professional service at all times</li><li>Undertake any other related task/duty/assignment that may be given by the superior</li></ul><p>**Newcomer Bonus, Variable Bonus, Merit Increment & Promotion, Staff Discount, Full Attendance Award, Referral Scheme, Grooming Allowance, Dental Benefits, Insurance, Birthday Vouchers, Festive Gift** <em>(Terms & Conditions apply)</em></p>",
